Hangout with Dolphins 🐬 in @metaquest ⬇️

We are excited to announce that first in the series of Ocean of Light productions is now live on Meta Quest TV. In spite of poor conditions that yielded very few shooting days we were able to create an extraordinarily immersive dolphin experience that places the viewer in the pod providing an intimate glimpse into life as a dolphin. This was a small production that relied heavily on the passion and commitment of our production and post production crews as well as the unwavering support from our Meta team. To all involved we extend my deep gratitude and appreciation. For those of you who have Meta Quest headsets you can find a link in my bio. For those who don’t, be sure to add a Meta Quest 3 to your holiday wish list! BTS to come in future posts.

Many thanks to:
 @metahorizon @echeng @jgleit @bschnarr @deepleigh Justin Browning @secret_steve @cliffeidelman Penka Kouneva @dneg @primefocustechnologies @impossibleacoustic @pinkishmercury @hugh.hou @keeley.ann.turner Fabricio Di Santo @heindl_cinema @hydroflexinc @backscattervideophoto @marmediacinemarentals @biminiscubacenter
